race.comment: WHERE'S IVY (8) goes very well at the distance with three wins and a placing from six starts. Recorded a 5.5 lengths win (20.52) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Appeals as a leading chance in this. CUMBRIA CHRISSY (6) has a strong record this trip including three wins from four starts. Scored by 1.75 lengths last time (20.62) in a Grade 5 over 365m at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. KUNG FU BAY (2) hit the frame latest (21.04) when second at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has already won three times from this draw. Suited here and expected to run well. PAR THREE (1) hit the frame here last start and can sneak into the finish again.
